name: gyroscopic effect
description: Skiboarders are always in motion. In the air, they experience what is known as the gyroscopic effect. Knowing about, and how to control this phenomena is key to skill and style. American Apparel California Fleece Pull-Over Hoody with a screen-printed gyroscope graphic of Revel8 rider, Kirk Thompson, in the center. Hoody price includes S&H to U.S. addresses. Only Medium and Large left!

name: collaboration
description: Enurshia’s next offering is a joint effort with SBOL, REVEL8, and Skiboard Magazine. This shirt includes web addresses as well as logos from your favorite brands. Show the world where you go to get the goods on our sport! Once again we are using American Apparel clothing because of the superior quality of their fabrics as well as their socially conscious business model. While this makes the shirts a little more expensive to produce, we feel it is worth it. Just ask anyone with our hoody and they’ll tell you the fabric choice really makes a difference. Price includes shipping and handling to U.S. Addresses. X-Large is sold out.

name: LAME
description: It’s just how we feel. Price includes shipping and handling to U.S. Addresses. VERY Limited quantities

name: Burton 420
description:
Black crush resistant case with watertight stitching on zipper. Small pouch with Velcro closure, an elastic loop, and a zippered bag that buttons on the inside to hold your goodies until you need them.

If you don’t know what this is for, you probably don’t need it.
